    "result": {"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Himanshu Mishra (@OrkoHunter)","description":"Personal website and blog of Himanshu Mishra (@OrkoHunter)","author":"@OrkoHunter","siteUrl":"https://orkohunter.net"}},"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f0d3d55e0329b720331a068b6e7e97fa/78d47/deleted.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.44444444444444%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/f0d3d55e0329b720331a068b6e7e97fa/7c297/deleted.webp 180w,\n/static/f0d3d55e0329b720331a068b6e7e97fa/33ecc/deleted.webp 360w,\n/static/f0d3d55e0329b720331a068b6e7e97fa/df77d/deleted.webp 720w,\n/static/f0d3d55e0329b720331a068b6e7e97fa/cf465/deleted.webp 800w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/f0d3d55e0329b720331a068b6e7e97fa/e9ea2/deleted.png 180w,\n/static/f0d3d55e0329b720331a068b6e7e97fa/53918/deleted.png 360w,\n/static/f0d3d55e0329b720331a068b6e7e97fa/242a6/deleted.png 720w,\n/static/f0d3d55e0329b720331a068b6e7e97fa/78d47/deleted.png 800w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/f0d3d55e0329b720331a068b6e7e97fa/242a6/deleted.png\"\n            alt=\"deleted\"\n            title=\"deleted\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>After letting Facebook Inc. build a vast profile of me for 9 years, I deleted my facebook account. Privacy is not my <em>only</em> concern, but I <a href=\"https://medium.com/@OrkoHunter/the-discovery-of-pseudo-acquaintance-9f903601d916\">personally reacted</a> to how Facebook has affected <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2017/12/20/16800842/facebook-2017-russia-scandal-news-feed-criticism-defectors\">the way we interact in our real life</a>.</p>\n<h3>How?</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Downloaded a copy of my data from facebook -> settings\nThis contained all of my messages, photos, videos, and probably a lot more information which I can not consciously recall sharing with Facebook.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Created a dummy facebook account* and added it to the resourceful groups I might miss out important information from.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><em>*An account without any interaction i.e. No likes, No reactions neither love nor angry, no comments, no photos/videos, no “friends”. A profile to just receive information on email (sent by facebook).</em></p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/help/delete_account\">https://www.facebook.com/help/delete_account</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>(Going extreme) Blocked Facebook servers on my computer that my computer can never communicate to domain names linked to Facebook servers. See <a href=\"https://github.com/jmdugan/blocklists/tree/master/corporations/facebook\">the list</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3><strong>Why?</strong></h3>\n<h4>Social concerns</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>People started using Facebook as LinkedIn by adding Freinds and it blurred the lines of relationships between two individuals — <a href=\"https://medium.com/@OrkoHunter/the-discovery-of-pseudo-acquaintance-9f903601d916\">Article</a></li>\n<li>Real addiction to unreal things — <a href=\"https://youtu.be/3ev7GXzFTPg?t=3m10s\">Video</a></li>\n<li>Facebook (read <em>Social Media</em>) promotes Ignorance by thoughtless comments, replies and reactions</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Privacy concerns</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>This will suffice — <a href=\"https://stallman.org/facebook.html\">https://stallman.org/facebook.html</a></li>\n</ul>","timeToRead":2,"frontmatter":{"categories":["Tech","Non-Tech"],"date":"Mar 25, 2018","draft":false,"slug":"/blog/delete-facebook","subtitle":"","summary":"","title":"#DeleteFacebook","image":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"src":"/static/f0d3d55e0329b720331a068b6e7e97fa/497c6/deleted.png"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"id":"f63e11f2-791b-57e4-a1dd-9eb70b55e096","frontmatter__slug":"/blog/delete-facebook","__params":{"frontmatter__slug":"blog"}}},
